OL,3,COff-duty police officer dismissed
OL,4,Cafter assaulting man and pushing child
OL,6,FA Staffordshire Police officer has
OL,7,Fbeen dismissed without notice, after
OL,8,Fassaulting a man and pushing a child
OL,9,Ffollowing a disagreement in a
OL,10,Fneighbour's garden, while he was off-
OL,11,Fduty.
OL,13,FThe officer, who was granted
OL,14,Fanonymity, was dismissed after a three-
OL,15,Fday independent misconduct hearing
OL,16,Ffound that his conduct amounted to
OL,17,Fgross misconduct.
