OL,6,FThe hearing concluded last Thursday (6
OL,7,FJune), and found the officer had
OL,8,Fbreached the standard relating to
OL,9,Fdiscreditable conduct.
OL,11,FThe officer will be placed on the
OL,12,Fnational College of Policing's Barred
OL,13,FList, which will prevent him from
OL,14,Fworking in policing and other law
OL,15,Fenforcement bodies.
OL,17,FDeputy Chief Constable Jon Roy said:
